name: Turquoise Blue Eye Sono Wood Plugs
description:
These plugs are made with Sono Wood(East Indian Rosewood) and feature my custom glass hand painted Turquoise Blue eye.

Please note that the Plugs will vary in size because they are made out of wood. I will try to match pairs as best I can.

These Plugs will be made to order, because of this they can take up to 7 days before they ship out.

These plugs ship USPS Priority Mail both within the U.S. and Internationally so you'll be sure to get your plugs quickly.

As with all organic body jewelry

~ Wood jewelry should only be worn in healed piercings. Do not use in freshly pierced ears. 
~ Avoid leaving plugs in direct sunlight. 
~ Always keep in dry and well-ventilated area. 
~ Organic material is heat and moisture sensitive and can warp, swell, or crack, if not cared for properly.

How to clean your wood plugs:

~ Wipe down your plugs with a damp cloth. Pat them dry, re-oil and allow to dry for a few hours. 
~ You can use Jojoba Oil or any other natural plant oil. You can also finish/polish them with natural beeswax.

If you buy more than one pair of plugs there are no additional shipping charges. Pay shipping for the first pair and any more you buy ship FREE.

If you have any questions feel free to use the contact page to send me an email.
